\begin_inset Formula $\theta_{1}=-1$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta_{2}=1$
\end_inset

,
 we obtain the solution 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta_{*}\left(t\right)=\sin t$
\end_inset

 and then trajectory 
\begin_inset Formula $q_{*}\left(t\right)$
\end_inset

 presented in
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
